text: Landmark 81 is a supertall skyscraper in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam. The investor and primary developer is Vinhomes, a Vietnamese company that is also the country's largest real-estate company. Landmark 81 is the tallest building in Vietnam, the second tallest building in Southeast Asia, and the 17th tallest building in the world. ==References== ==Other websites== *Landmark 81 SkyView Category:Buildings and structures in Vietnam Category:Ho Chi Minh City
